We really loved the gluten-free bread options. I have not had a sandwich in a long time.  It was so thick with turkey!

A very lovely restaurant with a salad bar (yes, really), open space, nice outdoor seating, and a comfortable bar area."}, {"review_date": "2021-12-28 21:02:56", "review_stars": 5.0, "review_text": "Savoy is impeccable.  Somehow every single item is delicious and fresh.  I always have a good experience.  The salad bar is for sure the best in the city.  The sandwiches, excellent.  The entrees, you guessed it, so good.  I would recommend them to anyone -- you gotta try it.  Note: closed Sundays!"}, {"review_date": "2021-12-22 20:28:32", "review_stars": 5.0, "review_text": "Great food and service! I don't live in the area, but next time I'm in Santa Barbara,  I will definitely eat there."}], "state": "CA"}

